                    th.text-white(data-field='characters' data-formatter='charFormatter')
                      | Characters (ID | Level | Element | Unclaimed Exp | Stamina)
                    th.text-white(data-field='unclaimed' data-formatter='currFormatter')
                      | Unclaimed Skills
                    th.text-white(data-field='rewards' data-formatter='stakedFormatter')
                      | Staked Skills
                    th.text-white(data-field='balance' data-formatter='currFormatter')
                      | Balance
                    th.text-white(data-field='action')
                      | Action
                tbody.text-center